{{Unreferenced|date=March 2018}}

'''''Direcção Nacional de Estatística''''' ([[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] for National Directorate of Statistics) or '''DNE''' is the national bureau for [[statistics]] of [[East Timor]]. The organization, a state department under the Directorate-General of Analysis and Research of the [[Ministry of Finance (East Timor)|Ministry of Finance]], is responsible for compiling and disseminating data on the people, society, economy and environment of the nation and the national [[Census|censuses]].

